  <description><![CDATA[<p>Take a journey through the Fjords, starting from the World Heritage city of <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen">Bergen</a> and ending in the capital city of <a data-udi="umb://document/4c3abf6ce2194dfe8f13f1fea46fd3d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c3abf6ce2194dfe8f13f1fea46fd3d5}" title="Oslo">Oslo</a>. Travel on panoramic trains, ferries and railways to really experience the breath-taking nature that Norway has to offer. Being able to experience one of the most picturesque rail journey's in the world, the Fl<span>å</span>m Railway, is a real highlight of this tour. </p>
<p> </p>
